divs: sighting detailsi was at the lake, camping with my family, i couldn't sleep that night, my head was hurting. i few hours after just looking through the window, i saw 3 yellow\orange lights hovering, i first thought it was a plane, but there was no plane noise, only a slight hum. then a slight outline appeared around the lights, i looked closer and took my camera out but then it started flying away, in a zig-zag type motion, first up, then backwards and down, then up again a few times, i couldn't get the camera started, so i just looked at it, and it started dissolving away, or faded.
Summary: A disc like shape with 4 orange lights flying up, in a zig-zag motion
